6010001.m_mFashionDes:
"Once a mark of slavery, now cherished as a badge of liberty.
Should they cast him into the furnace, he will rise as a flame to engulf the world in ruin."

6012001.m_mFashionDes:
"He gave everything for the light.
Yet in the end, he became the deepest shadow, forever denied by the radiance he sought."

6013001.m_mFashionDes: "Carrying the pride of the Ganelon family, Hati lingers in shadow, like a lotus veiled in darkness, waiting to bloom."

6016001.m_mFashionDes:
"Beneath the white veil, maiden's cheeks glow with blush.
Neither time nor death can touch her untarnished heart."

6018001.m_mFashionDes: "To reach the apex, he would pay any price. Even if it meant shedding the blood of former allies; even if all glory had faded."

6023001.m_mFashionDes:
"Please keep your shiny things, wallet, and soul safe!
If they vanish, it's none's falut.
Meow? You saw me take them? Cheeky to blame a cat for that."

6029001.m_mFashionDes:
"The sea breeze carries the scent of fine wine, painting golden dreams under the Sapphire Isle sunset.
Sweet as it is, don't lose your wits."

6062001.m_mFashionDes:
"This sleeping beauty escaped the castle that imprisoned her, only to find the world outside covered in thorns.
Raked with wounds, she holds her lantern high to light the path forward in this endless night."
